v:4 c:$ m:portfolio role:dev x:vue-router-transitions
gate: OPEN

task: Build app shell with vue-router and animated page-transitions. Shell hosts loader (T08), bottom-nav (port from sdui-proto L631-654), and `<router-view>` with view-transition + GSAP enter/leave.

requires: [vue, vite]
out:
  - app/src/router/index.ts
  - app/src/router/routes.ts
  - app/src/layouts/AppShell.vue
  - app/src/layouts/BottomNav.vue
  - app/src/transitions/PageTransition.vue
  - app/src/views/Hero.vue (placeholder)
  - app/src/views/Work.vue (placeholder)
  - app/src/views/Lab.vue (placeholder)
  - app/src/views/Contact.vue (placeholder)

cmd:
  - cd app && pnpm add vue-router@4

routes (concept-agnostic skeleton):
  - / → Hero
  - /work → Work
  - /lab → Lab
  - /contact → Contact
  (concept A/B/C will repurpose these in S02 — Hero == playground/timeline/constellation)

constraints:
  - Use View Transitions API where supported, fallback to GSAP fade+blur.
  - BottomNav active-indicator uses `nav-indicator` keyframe from sdui.css L649-654.
  - AppShell layout: `app-content-wrapper` → `app-router-wrapper` → `<router-view>` → `BottomNav` (matches sdui.css L622-637).
  - Route changes log to `room_dwell` (T04 schema) on unmount with elapsed ms.

done:
  - All 4 routes navigate without flash; transition < 400ms.
  - BottomNav highlights active route with glow-indicator.
  - Tab switching writes a row to `room_dwell` (verified in Studio).
  - Reduced-motion preference disables GSAP transition (a11y).
